description:
C# wrapper library for the Trakt.tv API.

Features
- Full Trakt.tv API Coverage
- Authentication Support (OAuth 2.0 and Device)
- Completely asynchronous
- API Environments (Production and Sandbox)
- Serialization Service
- Language Service
